== Class Spell Lists ==

=== Hero Spells ===

The Hero learns a mix of healing, lightning, and utility:
* Healing line (Heal → Healmore → Healus)
* Zap line (exclusive)
* Travel spells (Return, Outside, Repel)

=== Mage Spells ===

Pure offensive magic:
* Fire line (Blaze series)
* Ice line (Icebolt series)
* Explosion line (Bang series)
* Debuffs and status

=== Priest Spells ===

Healing and support:
* Full healing line
* Resurrection
* Buffs (Upper, Bikill)
* Anti-undead (Beat, Defeat)

=== Sage Spells ===

The Sage learns BOTH Mage and Priest spells:
* All Mage spells
* All Priest spells
* Most versatile caster

== Spell Learning Levels ==

Spells are learned at specific levels for each class. After class change, previous spells are retained while new class spells are learned fresh.

